reviews.text:

Chain noodle shop around Hong Kong. Famous for hiring new immigrants from China which makes them socially responsible. Don't expect the best service there cos ppl are loud! Food wise, their food are always great and up to their standard. You can expect the same taste in all branches.

The only decent place for food in TKL.
Tasty and spicy noodles, and reasonably priced. 
Choice of toppings. Tofu skin and pork is my favourite!
